{
  "id": "adv_event_2602_01_02",
  "title": "センターへの想い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の深夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.4199999332999997,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.3332618
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "渚、何してるの？\nもしかして、眠れない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6333332618,
      "endTime": 8.2875507911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。ちょっとだけ考えごと\n月ストのこと……っていうか、琴乃ちゃんのことを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4999999285,
      "endTime": 17.0278680086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "え……私のこと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.240317146,
      "endTime": 19.694920388899998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。次の新曲で着るのはバレンタインの衣装でしょ？\n可愛い系だと思うし、琴乃ちゃん似合うだろうな～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9069838126,
      "endTime": 28.9069836217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "もう、冗談ばっかり……\n本当は、別のことなんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0860987901,
      "endTime": 34.7858949898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、さすがにバレちゃうか～\n……さっき、センターの話を聞いて、改めて思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9860990444,
      "endTime": 45.106847373600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "きっと今まで琴乃ちゃんは、センターとして\nいろんなことを考えてくれてたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2859636862,
      "endTime": 53.655169924000006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "一番注目される分、一番頑張らなきゃいけないし\n責任も感じるだろうし、逃げる訳にもいかないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8676190614,
      "endTime": 63.2676194428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなからの期待はもちろん\nライブバトルのプレッシャーだって、物凄くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4467395703,
      "endTime": 71.9244038502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "今回みたいに、大きなお仕事が重なる中でも\nきっと手を抜かず、一人で背負ってきたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1368529875,
      "endTime": 80.8053107817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、そうだったかもしれない……\nでも、今は違うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0177599191,
      "endTime": 87.68993656629999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなと、すずが照らしてくれるから\n私は一人じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8844265858,
      "endTime": 94.2999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう。その言葉が聞けて良かったよ\nでも、そっかぁ。ふ～ん。すずちゃんね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6844255685,
      "endTime": 106.1251964807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ……？　な、なんで拗ねてるの……？\n私、変なこと言ったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3376456181,
      "endTime": 112.9123848836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "別に拗ねてないも～ん\n拗ねてないけど……うん。そうだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1043122847,
      "endTime": 121.87052551100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "（今は、すずちゃんもセンターとして立ってくれてる）\n（一人が大変な時は、もう一人が引っ張って、輝いて）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0829746484,
      "endTime": 132.20703318099999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "（それなら、今回みたいに『二人』が大変な時は）\n（誰かが立たなきゃ……ううん、『私』が立ちたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4194823185,
      "endTime": 143.6990422168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "（私自身の強さ。私自身の道。まだ、それは）\n（分からないけど、それでも。誰よりも輝きたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9114913541,
      "endTime": 156.98906493959998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 158.0488847414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "（今度は、琴乃ちゃんのかわりじゃなくて）\n（一人のアイドルとして）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1348484276,
      "endTime": 164.8032385109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、琴乃ちゃん\nお話し出来て良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.9823471942,
      "endTime": 171.6309866824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "いつも話してるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.8434358197,
      "endTime": 173.7234358626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "今日は特別なの\n……もう少しだけ、こうしてよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9101024864,
      "endTime": 179.34352629159997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2226441302,
      "endTime": 181.3559672909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "それでは早速、昨日の答えを聞かせてくださいまし\nこの中で、新曲のセンターに立候補――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.2559672909,
      "endTime": 190.8113872128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい\n白石沙季、センターに立候補します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.889299607,
      "endTime": 195.0666575114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "わー！？　沙季ちゃんズルい！\n芽衣も芽衣も！　芽衣も、センターに立候補するよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.1501594461,
      "endTime": 202.3901595033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。じゃあ、みんなライバルだね\n私も立候補するよ、琴乃ちゃん、すずちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.6026086406,
      "endTime": 210.55260873600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "聞くまでもなかったですわね\n当然、私も立候補いたしますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.7650578734,
      "endTime": 217.74006903140003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん私も。ふふ、{user}さんにも\n伝えておくわね。みんな、手加減なしでいきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.9317245401,
      "endTime": 226.5489576258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "本番では、新曲のデモに合わせて、それぞれが\nセンターを交代で担当してみて、スコアを比べる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.7317174193,
      "endTime": 237.7946530578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
