      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "新曲が出来るまでは、今ある曲で練習しようかな？\nあ、他のグループのバレンタイン曲も参考になるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.0071021952,
      "endTime": 248.1885929026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "よーし！　そしたら次は、この曲で踊ってみよっと！\nどんな曲でもいいように、一杯練習しないとね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.4010420399,
      "endTime": 256.8700445729,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8781.451670399974
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "気合いが入っていますわねぇ、芽衣\nなんだかいつもよりも真剣じゃありませんこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.0824937103,
      "endTime": 264.23560020900004,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15757.494082599977
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　芽衣はいつも真剣だよ？　でも確かに、今回は\n特にやる気満々かも！　ほらほら、見て、すずにゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.449160377,
      "endTime": 274.3663583674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの？　スケジュール帳なんて見せて\n……って、朝も夜も練習の予定がびっしり！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.5788075048,
      "endTime": 284.9290966588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "凄いでしょ～。しっかり自主練の予定を組んだんだよ！\nドーナツ屋さんへ行く時間も削ったんだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.1121204931,
      "endTime": 292.5675646383,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11387.869334299978
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣とは思えない程のスパルタですわね\n私と駄菓子屋さんに行く日も削っているようですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.7800137757,
      "endTime": 300.3204179048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　あっ、ほ、本当だ！\nあわわ、さすがにそれは組み直さないとだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.5133430401,
      "endTime": 308.44517964519997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、まったく芽衣らしいというかなんというか\nでも、どうしてそこまでセンターになりたいんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.4909539779,
      "endTime": 319.5985053619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふー、それはね～、あ～、えっとぉ……\nすずにゃんには秘密！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.7909539779,
      "endTime": 328.9227000793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！？　気になる言い方しないでくださいまし！\nどうして私には秘密なんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 329.1351492167,
      "endTime": 336.350818181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、いろいろあるんだよ～\nでも、芽衣は本気だよ。今回は絶対に負けないからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.5351492167,
      "endTime": 345.153745103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで言うなら構いません。競い合う\n相手の事情をとやかく聞くなんて無粋ですものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 345.3661942404,
      "endTime": 353.2061942022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "なら私がやることは一つ。全力で迎え撃って\nやりますわ！　かかってきなさい、芽衣！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.3995275737,
      "endTime": 362.7045181514,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9800.462253799993
        },
